title: BEAUTIFUL FURNISHED IN PARAMOUNT WORLD!!
posting_body: ['Fully Furnished Residence.', 'Impeccable 2BD+Den/3BA with 02 side-by-side parking spaces.', 'The 09 line is the best and most desired line for a 2-bedroom in the building.', 'Features include southeast exposure with plenty of natural light and fantastic views; 10ft ceilings; upgrade Italian flooring; large square-shaped balcony aka outdoor living room; European kitchen and lush bathrooms.', 'The Paramount is the building with the most amenities in the world and sits on top of the Miami World Center, the 2nd largest urban development in the US.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
